title: S. Jaishankar
added: Jaishankar was appointed as [[Foreign Secretary of India|Foreign Secretary]] of India on 29 January 2015. The announcement of his appointment was made following a 28 January 2015 meeting of the Appointments Committee of the Cabinet chaired by the PM, [[Narendra Modi]].<ref name="BVMN">[http://pib.nic.in/newsite/eRelease.aspx?relid=115035 ACC Appointment], ''[[Press Information Bureau]]'', 29 January 2015</ref><ref name="BVML">[https://web.archive.org/web/20150128210444/http://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/india-s-ambassador-to-us-s-jaishankar-is-the-new-foreign-secretary/article1-1311595.aspx S Jaishankar, is the new foreign secretary], ''[[Hindustan Times]]'', 29 January 2015</ref> Jaishankar is widely credited by Nepalese analysts for being the "original planner of [[2015 Nepal blockade]]".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.onlinekhabar.com/2019/05/769938|title=नाकाबन्दीका योजनाकारलाई किन बनाइयो विदेशमन्त्री ?|access-date=4 June 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.onlinekhabar.com/2019/05/769772|title=नाकाबन्दीका डिजाइनर बने मोदी सरकारका मन्त्री|access-date=4 June 2019}}</ref>
